NG0208:2203: thugs kar rigs pa'i 'khor lo'i sngags //
NG0208:2204: rtsibs bzhi dbus na 'bru lnga'i mchog / lte bar 'byung ba'i 'khor gyi sngags //
NG0208:2205: rtsibs bzhir he dun ya dang a //
NG0208:2206: gsal bas stong gsum dbang du sdud //
NG0208:2207: 'khor lo rgyun gyi srung ba'i mchog / drag po sngags kyi dmod pa ni //
NG0208:2208: snying po ngang dang shugs kyis drangs //
NG0208:2209: rngam tshig drag la gtum pa'o //
NG0208:2210: sa na ga tsit+ta ro myags kha tham srog la gzir mnan sbur nan 'drid phyung hri shag rbad /
NG0208:2212: gsal bas bdag bsrung brtan pa'i mchog / 'di bzlas pa la dus rnam pa gnyis te /
NG0208:2214: rgyun du stong bzlas pa ni /
NG0208:2216: zhag lnga'am bdun du khri khri bzlas pa'i dus ni /
NG0208:2217: nam mkha' las thog ser dang lce 'bab pa'i dus dang */
NG0208:2218: sa g.yos dang rims rlangs dang thabs 'ong ba'i dus dang */
NG0208:2219: rbod gtong gi dam 'khrugs pa dang shi kha phye ba dang */
NG0208:2220: mdze rims me bzhin mched pa dang */
NG0208:2221: dus ma yin pa'i sgra dang */
NG0208:2222: chu dang mtshon dar ba'i dus bzlas pa ni /
NG0208:2223: drag la rtsub pa'i srung ba'o //
NG0208:2225: zor du pho nya slar la bzlog / 'khor lo mnan pa lto bar 'brel //
NG0208:2226: 'khyams shing slar log gsang lam gyis //
NG0208:2227: sngags kyi dug mda' khong nas 'phen //
NG0208:2228: srung ba'i rgyal po lus srog 'byed kyang spel ba min /
NG0208:2229: me rlung skyi 'dang 'khrugs pa'i rgyud las /
NG0208:2230: sngags dang dug mda' khong nas dbyung ba'i le'u ste nyi shu gsum pa'o ///
NG0208:2232: drag po sngags kyi gdug pa dug mda' khong nas dbyung ba ni /
NG0208:2233: zhal gyi dmod pa sngags dang ngan sngags rtsub mo'i nus pa zhugs pa ste /
NG0208:2234: de'i 'khrul 'khor drag po bca' ba ni //
NG0208:2235: thod pa bkra mi shis pa'am /
NG0208:2236: yang na thod pa dur ma'i spyi bor mu khyud bzhi ru bskor la //
NG0208:2237: dbus su gru gsum la gnod byed kyi ming khrag gis bri /
NG0208:2238: de'i phyi rim la gnod byed kyi ming khrag gis bris //
NG0208:2239: de'i phyi rim sbrul gyi chun po bri /
NG0208:2240: mtha' ma me ri nang du bstan pa bris la /
NG0208:2241: dong gru gsum gyi nang du gzhug thod pa gling
NG0208:2242: bzhi pa gcig gi nang du mu khyud bzhi ru
NG0208:2243: bskor la / dbus su dregs pa lnga'i snying po bri /
NG0208:2244: de'i phyi rim rtsibs bzhir byas la /
NG0208:2245: drag po stobs kyi klu bzhir dgod /
NG0208:2246: de'i phyir rim rtsibs brgyad la /
NG0208:2248: tha ma rtsibs bcu ru byas la /
NG0208:2249: dug mda' dbyung ba'i spu gri dgod /
NG0208:2250: thod pa 'og mar khrag sna lnga blugs la /
NG0208:2251: thod pa gnyis kha sbyar steng ma la /
NG0208:2252: thun khung btod la thun dbab pa ni /
NG0208:2253: rdo phye dang lcags phye dang zangs phye dang */
NG0208:2255: seng ldeng gi phur pa rnams la /
NG0208:2257: gang dmigs pa'i lus bdag gi 'og tu mnan la
NG0208:2258: phur pa dang thun rdzas brab kyin thod par bstim
NG0208:2259: mo // sngags kyang drag la bar ma chad par bzla /
NG0208:2260: thod pa'i 'khrul 'khor zhing gi me la bdug / man tra g+hu h+ya sarba dum nan /
NG0208:2262: khri tsho bcu'i las rdzogs nas /
NG0208:2264: gang dmigs pa'i bu ga rnams las khrag bton la /
NG0208:2265: thod pa 'og ma khyi nag po dom po dang */
NG0208:2269: dpa' bo gri ru bsad pa'i khrag de rnams blugs la dug gi chus sbyangs te /
NG0208:2270: nam gyi gung la gar gnod pa'i sa ru 'phang ngo *//
NG0208:2271: lan bdun nam dgu ru byas nas /
NG0208:2272: mthar thod pa'i steng 'og ma nor bar dkyil 'khor chen po'i 'og tu gnan pa byas na /
NG0208:2276: klu gnyan sa bdag gi dug nad rtsa la zhugs pa kun khong nas 'byin par 'gyur nus so //
NG0208:2277: dug mda' khong nas dbyung ba'i drag sngags /
NG0208:2278: drag po thod pa'i 'khor lo mngon du phyung ba'o //
NG0208:2279: gzhan bsrung ba dang thun mong du spyod na /

NG0208:2281: me rlung skyi 'dang 'khrugs pa'i rgyud las /
NG0208:2282: drag po thod pa mngon du phyung ba'i le'u ste
NG0208:2283: nyi shu bzhi pa'o // // dregs pa lnga'i zhal
NG0208:2284: gyi dmod pa / man ngag kun gyi rtsa ba /
NG0208:2285: bsgrub pa kun gyi snying bcud du phyung ba /
NG0208:2286: drag sngags thams cad kyi nying khu phrin las thams cad kyi mchog bsdus pa'o //
NG0208:2287: ngan sngags thams cad kyi rgyal po //
NG0208:2288: bdud kyi khong lto nye bar dril ba /
NG0208:2289: drag po btsan thabs kyi sngags rgod /
NG0208:2291: bsad pa kun gyi mchog bsdus pa'o //
NG0208:2292: rnal 'byor ba drang gsum dang ldan pa'i brtul zhugs rab 'byams kyi dbang thob pa /
NG0208:2293: thugs kyi man ngag zhal gyi yig chung thob par byas la /
NG0208:2294: las gang yang btsan thabs su nye bar brtsam par bya'o //
NG0208:2296: dur khrod dben pa'i bde gnas su //
NG0208:2297: rang sems dben pa'i mtshams bcad la //
NG0208:2298: dpa' brtul dmod pa'i drag sngags bzlas //
NG0208:2299: dur khrag rgyu la tsakra bca' //
NG0208:2300: mu khyud bzhi dang ldan par bskor //
NG0208:2301: lte bar gru gsum ma ra nr-i //
NG0208:2302: gnyis pa rgya gram e dun ka ya dgod //
NG0208:2303: gsum pa rdo rje'i rwa brgyad la //
NG0208:2304: srog la breng breng srog la gsum //
NG0208:2305: dun dun bzhi la srog la rbad dang lnga /
NG0208:2306: kham shag drug la rtsa la rbad dang bdun //
NG0208:2307: srog la zhes pa brgyad du dgod //
NG0208:2308: yang logs chu yi mu khyud la //
NG0208:2309: gang bsgrub bsad sngags lto sdeb dgod //
NG0208:2310: tha ma'i rgya gram rtsibs bcu la //
NG0208:2311: myogs dang rbad dang khyer dang phyung *//
NG0208:2312: mugs dang ting dang ling dang bshag / long dang rbad rnams re rer dgod //
NG0208:2313: srid pa'i rus sbal lto bar bca' //
NG0208:2314: kha sbyar tshar rdzas kyi yang gyi sbal par gzhug / de nas tshon skud phag mo'i ltor //
NG0208:2315: gnyan nam mchod rten nag po la //
NG0208:2316: nyin dang mtshan res gang brtsam 'grub //
NG0208:2317: phyag rgya zil gnon bsam gtan bsgom //
NG0208:2318: rang yang rang la gab par bshad //
NG0208:2319: me rlung skyi 'dang 'khrugs pa'i rgyud las /
NG0208:2320: phyag rgya bsam gtan gyi le'u ste nyer lnga pa'o ///
NG0208:2322: e dun ka yam dgra bo'i srog la breng breng srog la dun dun /
NG0208:2327: mugs ting ling shag long rbad /
NG0208:2328: a pa da ra yam rbad /
NG0208:2331: 'di ni kun gyi mchog bsdus pa sa yin pas snang snang mi brtsam /
NG0208:2332: nag po yi ni dkar po'i bdam //
NG0208:2333: tha chung bzhi la dus tshod bdam //
NG0208:2334: rgyun gyi khong lto yin pas kun la mi 'phyar //
NG0208:2335: brtul zhugs rab kyi spyad la gzhan @#//
NG0208:2337: drag sngags tshad dang ldan par chu bo'i rka mi gcad //
NG0208:2338: sems kyi drod la brtag cing rmi lam rtags la min //
NG0208:2339: dmar len khri bzlas phyag rgya yang gsal gdab //
NG0208:2340: som nyi le lo mi bya tshogs dang gtor ma min //
NG0208:2341: the tshom g.yeng ba med la dam rdzas brten mi dgos //
NG0208:2342: dge ba rgyun ma gcad par skul tshig g.yeng ba med //
NG0208:2343: 'khor lo thod par bcas pa rgya yis gzir ba yin //
NG0208:2344: sa sros klu gzir phyogs su rngam pas bgrod //
NG0208:2345: dmigs pa phyin nas mgo gzhug dril zhing gzir //
NG0208:2346: ral gri phyag mtshan lto bzhi bshags la bskor //
NG0208:2347: thod stan dang bcas gru dong sbas la bcag / 'byung ba bzhi dang ri rab pho brang bskyed //
NG0208:2348: rgya gram steng du las kyi rgyal pos gnan //
NG0208:2349: brgya bzlas rang gi phyag rgya bsam gtan bsgom /
NG0208:2350: kha gso mtha' ru 'phya ma ha yis 'phang *//
NG0208:2351: rang lus rdo rje'i go gon gzhan gyi mtshon cha kha snyil //
NG0208:2352: phyag rgya brtan pa'i dbang thob rkyen gyis shigs mi srid //
NG0208:2353: mtshon cha'i rgyal po dmar len gzhan gyi lus srog 'bral //
NG0208:2354: srid pa gdug pa'i ltor chud 'chor zhing 'gyur mi srid //
NG0208:2355: drag po srog gcod yin pas sprul pa bla ma'i khyab //
NG0208:2356: rdzu 'phrul stobs las skyes pa'i gdams ngag drag po gab //
NG0208:2357: me rlung skyi 'dang 'khrugs pa'i rgyud las /
NG0208:2358: mtshon cha'i rgyal po dmar len gzhan gyi lus srog 'bral ba'i le'i ste nyer drug pa'o ///
NG0208:2359: / de nas yang bcom ldan 'das kyis /
NG0208:2360: drag sngags kyi de kho na nyid /
NG0208:2361: srog dmar len gyi sbyor ba /
NG0208:2362: bcom ldan 'das dpal tshe bdag nag po'i snying po
NG0208:2363: don gyi man ngag las khyad par dmar len drag
NG0208:2364: po ni / bdag don thabs kyis grol ba'i las //
NG0208:2365: ba dang 'o ma zho dang mar //
NG0208:2366: zhun mar snum gyi snying po'i tshul //
NG0208:2367: snying po sbyor ba bsad dang gso //
NG0208:2368: bsad gso khyad par sbyor ba dag / g.yeng med bstan dang grol dbang gces //
NG0208:2369: stobs dang sbyor ba'i snying phyung 'di //
NG0208:2370: gong mthun rgyu la tsakra bca' //
NG0208:2371: rdzas dang thang pa'i sbyor ba min //
NG0208:2372: dpa' brtul drag po'i stobs kyis spyad //
NG0208:2373: gdug byed phag mo'i lto ba ru //
NG0208:2374: srid pa'i khyams khang srog sdud bca' /
NG0208:2375: khyams khang lte bar brnag pa'i gzugs //
NG0208:2376: ming gzugs snying gar mtshon cha bri //
NG0208:2377: phyi rim rgya gram rtsa ba'i sngags //
NG0208:2378: yang logs bcu gnyis spu gri dgod //
NG0208:2379: rus sbal lto ba'i phyogs mtshams la //
NG0208:2380: rtsibs chen bcu gnyis rtse mo na //
NG0208:2381: bsad pa drag po'i spu gri ldan //
NG0208:2382: phag mo'i lto na rtsibs bcu gnyis //
NG0208:2383: rtse mo nang bstan spu gri dgod //
NG0208:2384: 'khrul mig khyams khang ming rus gang *//
NG0208:2385: don gnyis bsdus la sbyor ba bskul /
NG0208:2386: kha sbyor thod pa dong rtsa bcal //
NG0208:2387: rgyu rkyen drug gi rten bcas la //
NG0208:2388: thod par bcug la mthing nag dgab //
NG0208:2389: bsgom bskul drag sngags bsnol mar bskul //
NG0208:2390: rab kyi rkang thon bsnol mar gcod //
NG0208:2393: rang sngags phag mo'i spu gri brdegs //
NG0208:2394: dbugs kyi rtar bskyon yul la 'phang *//
NG0208:2395: gsang lam sgo dgu rtsa la 'jug / rang bdud gshed ma rang las ldang *//
NG0208:2397: lus srog dwangs snyigs 'byed cing sdud //
NG0208:2398: sku lnga dz+nya na pany+tsar smin //
NG0208:2399: 'gyur med rtags stobs dpag tu med //
NG0208:2400: snyigs ma'i yi ge rten la dbab //
NG0208:2401: rig pa bde ba'i klong la 'pho //
NG0208:2402: dmar len bskyed pa'i khong nas srog / tsit+ta dkar nag zhun thabs tshul //
NG0208:2403: brnag pa'i rten ni zhu zhing khol //
NG0208:2404: tsa na'i 'bras bus len cing sdud //
NG0208:2405: sdud pa'i yi ge gsum dang ldan //
NG0208:2406: ya yis 'phul sbyor ra yis bsreg / thod par snying po bcud bsdus byas //
NG0208:2408: yi ge byin cing rten du brtag / steng 'og
NG0208:2409: tshangs pa'i rtsa la brtag / rten can klu gzir
NG0208:2410: gdug pa gtad // klu las bcud spangs 'grin zlar gtad //
NG0208:2411: gzhan du lha yi snying po bcud //
NG0208:2412: 'gyur med brtan pa stobs dpag med //
NG0208:2413: ha la khang zhes dus la mtho //
NG0208:2414: sprul sku phyag rgya sku bsam yas //
NG0208:2415: thob cing bgrod pa sngags kyi stobs //
NG0208:2417: e myags ya rngubs mugs shag ka dun dgra bo hur thum dza /
NG0208:2418: rtsa khrag snying thum ril rak+sha rbad /
NG0208:2421: mchod sbyor ba'i stobs zhan nas //
NG0208:2422: stobs chen drag po nang rgyas na //
NG0208:2423: drag sngags yon tan gnyis su bskyed //
NG0208:2424: mi gcod 'gyangs na dkrugs nas spogs //
NG0208:2425: e myags ya rngubs sbubs ya dun shag srog thum ram dza la /
NG0208:2426: hur rtsa khrag dmar snying thum rbad thum /
NG0208:2427: snying po man ngag kun gcod 'di //
NG0208:2429: b+hu ti b+ha ni ma nor yin //
NG0208:2430: ta tha ga yi glang po rta yi mchog / ka ma ra tsa ma ra na /
NG0208:2431: ha la ka la tsa ma ri //
NG0208:2432: ru tra tir ti ma ra ya //
NG0208:2433: nr-i kar ma byed b+ha sa ra //
NG0208:2434: g+hu ha sa ba'i mchog bsdus 'di //
NG0208:2435: rang gi snying la so phag tham //
NG0208:2436: me rlung skyi 'dang 'khrugs pa'i rgyud las /
NG0208:2437: khyad par dmar len gyi sbyor ba'i le'u ste nyer bdun pa'o ///
NG0208:2438: / de nas bcom ldan 'das kyi seng ge'i khog par shig pa'i sbyor ba 'di gsungs so //
NG0208:2439: byin chen bde ba'i gsang gnas su //
NG0208:2440: gsang ba mchog gi sbyor ba brtsam //
NG0208:2441: b+hi la khong 'dus khong dregs can //
NG0208:2442: ha la nag po ya ma'i klong *//
NG0208:2443: be ga ta yi 'jig rten na //
NG0208:2444: ya ma rak+sha'i bde klong du //
NG0208:2445: sgyu ma'i snying po'i gnas sbyangs la //
NG0208:2446: thugs kyi bde ba gnyis med spro //
NG0208:2447: de yi sbyor ba 'di lta ste //
NG0208:2448: 'dul khrims nyams pa'i gos blangs la //
NG0208:2449: rdo lcags zangs phye dug chus bsku //
NG0208:2450: cha gnyis byas la thig gdab brtsam //
NG0208:2451: zil gnon phyag rgya dpang gzug bsam //
NG0208:2452: drag sngags dmod pa stod du sbyar //
NG0208:2453: tha chung bzhi yi mar ngo la //
NG0208:2455: dbus nas thig skor bzhi ru @#//
NG0208:2457: dbus su gru gsum bde gnas su //
NG0208:2458: sku yi gzugs brnyan bris la ming *//
NG0208:2459: zla gam gsum las srung ba'i lha //
NG0208:2460: phyi rim bcu gnyis gsang ba'i sngags //
NG0208:2462: nr-i dang phyi nang gong ma bzhin //
NG0208:2463: mtha' ma'i 'khrul mig bcu drug la //
NG0208:2464: gsod cing gnon pa'i spu gri dgod //
NG0208:2465: srid pa'i rus sbal lto na gnas //
NG0208:2466: dug dang khrag gis ngar blud la //
NG0208:2467: rje'am yul srung thod par gzhug / rtsang bcas dong du mthing nag dgab //
NG0208:2468: dmigs med ngang las ye shes kyi //
NG0208:2469: rol pa phyag rgya chen por 'phro //
NG0208:2470: drag tu bskul kyin shugs kyis 'phang *//
NG0208:2471: mkha' khyab rdo rje'i sbyor bas te //
NG0208:2472: dmod pa'i lus la spu gri gdags //
NG0208:2473: ming rus mi sbyar khyams la bcad //
NG0208:2474: rgya mdud brtsegs pa'i lto ru gnan //
NG0208:2475: yang na dkyil 'khor chen pa yi //
NG0208:2476: 'og tu bka' yi byin bsdus la //
NG0208:2477: rin po che yi lto ru gnan //
NG0208:2478: bshags dang dge ba rgyud mi gcad //
NG0208:2479: 'byung ba lnga yi dwangs bsdus la //
NG0208:2480: rin po che yi rgyas par bstan //
NG0208:2481: rgyu yi snyigs ma'i srog bsdus la //
NG0208:2482: dbus kyi 'bub gnas gzugs la bstim //
NG0208:2483: sa dang chu dang me dang rlung *//
NG0208:2484: nam mkha'i dbyings kyi khongs su gzhug / dmigs pa dag pa'i tshad ma gdon //
NG0208:2485: de nas bcom ldan 'das kyis nyid kyi sku gsung
NG0208:2486: thugs las ye shes sngags kyi spu gri bton to
NG0208:2487: // g+hu ru nr-i srog myogs thum ril rbad /
NG0208:2489: bgrod pa med pa'i phyag rgyar bstan //

NG0208:2493: / de nas yang bcom ldan 'das kyis drag sngags gnam lcags kyi sbyor ba 'di bshad do //
NG0208:2494: rang sems dben pa'i gnas mchog tu //
NG0208:2495: dam tshig mchog gi mtshams bcad la //
NG0208:2496: zhing ras lpags shun khru gang la //
NG0208:2497: sbyor ba'i rgyal po gsum sbyar la //
NG0208:2498: mchog dang ldan par rgya bcad la //
NG0208:2499: zhing gi srad bus thig gdab brtsam //
NG0208:2500: dbus nas thig skor lnga ru drang *//

NG0208:2503: dbus su gru gsum drag po'i gnas //
NG0208:2504: de yi phyi rim gsum pa la //
NG0208:2505: phyogs bzhir thig rkang gsum du drang *//

NG0208:2512: de na gnas pa'i rim pa ni //
NG0208:2513: dbus dang mtshams bzhir dmigs bya'i ming *//
NG0208:2514: dri ma dang bcas tshe srog sdud //
NG0208:2515: phyogs bzhi'i 'khrul mig bcu drug la //
NG0208:2516: thun dang gsod pa'i spu gri @#//
NG0208:2518: yang logs 'khrul mig bcu drug la //
NG0208:2519: rtsa ba'i drag sngags 'bru bcu gnyis //

NG0208:2523: de bzhin rgyan gyi bcu gsum la //
NG0208:2524: gcod cing gnon pa'i spu gri ldan //
NG0208:2525: lnga pa tha ma'i bzhi bcu la //
NG0208:2526: thun bzhi sngags kyi sbyor ba gnas //
NG0208:2527: gang byed sngags dang sbyar la bzlas //
NG0208:2528: gang chu myos pa sbyor bskul bsdug kha sbyar rgya chen sngon dmar la //
NG0208:2529: sngags pa rtsa lnga'i thod pa ru //

NG0208:2531: rtsa byabs lha bsgom dmod pa bzlas //
